title: Frogtown house for rent
posting_body: ['Frog town house for rent ($2400/month)', 'A detached back house located near LA River bike path and Dodger Stadium.', 'A quiet neighborhood, and only a few minutes’ drive to Downtown LA, China town, Silverlake, and Highland Park.', ' Close to USC Health Sciences Campus, Union Station, Arts District, and Griffith Park.', 'Easy access to 5, 10, 110, and 2 freeways.', 'Great for couple or single person.', '1 bedroom, 1 bath, plus an office space', 'Refrigerator', 'Gas range oven and hood', 'Quartz countertop', 'Washer/dryer in-unit', 'Window air conditioning', 'Laminate floors throughout', 'Ceramic tile in kitchen area', 'New paint', 'Private patio space', 'A single space garage storage', 'One off-street parking', 'DETAILS', 'Deposit 1 month rent', 'Tenant to pay all utilities', 'No smoking of any kind', 'No dog, cat ok', 'Rental insurance required', 'REQUIREMENTS: (To be accompanied with application)', '1) Current/last 3 months proof of income/statements showing year-to-date earnings, deductions, monthly net earnings (ck stubs and bank statements)', '2) Application fee required']
